  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>Sleeps: 10 Guests.</strong></p>
<p>Chalet 'Red Riding Hood' has a superb location in the heart of the resort, just a short walk from the main Medran lifts for speedy access to the skiing, and Place Centrale with its array of bars and cafes.</p>
<p>The spacious chalet has an open-plan living and dining room where breakfast, afternoon tea and cake and dinner is served, and also boasts a large balcony with lovely views over the valley. The 5 twin rooms all have private facilities adjacent or en suite, and provide a comfortable base in an ideal location to explore all that Verbier has to offer.</p>]]></description>
